{"type": "article", "id": 27094, "title": "“象耳”灯", "description": "", "date": "2016-05-20T06:55:30Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 19, "image": "img/article/article_show/201607021105199jqGxDVoaEemrg4s.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>以著名的童话系列《大象艾玛》为灵感，设计师 <a href=\"http://www.guillaumedelvigne.com/\">Guillaume Delvigne</a> 联手法国 <a href=\"http://bellila.fr/fr/\">Bellila</a> 工作室推出了与故事主角同名的台灯 Elmer。这个小小的台灯有一个橡木制成的坚固底座和一对好像翅膀的金属“大耳”，可以帮助它轻松地搭在搁板上。你可以通过链接购买这款小巧可爱的台灯，售价为 225 欧元。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702110517HautDLpKMWUdxfR1.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702110517Aea5V7IW2tQcH48k.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702110518mbQ2BRtwoFsGLd0Y.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.505\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702110518Byr2EJ8ACT3WejoD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}